Previous month same dates
mssql - [Date] >= DATEADD(MONTH, DATEDIFF(MONTH, 0, GETDATE()) - 1, 0)
AND [Date] <= DATEADD(MONTH, -1, CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE))

Previous month
ms sql - [Date] >= DATEADD(MONTH, DATEDIFF(MONTH, 0, GETDATE())-1, 0)
AND [Date] < DATEADD(MONTH, DATEDIFF(MONTH, 0, GETDATE()), 0)

MTD
MS SQL - [Date] >= DATEADD(MONTH, DATEDIFF(MONTH, 0, GETDATE()), 0)
AND [Date] < DATEADD(DAY, 1, CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE))
